These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, snake, frog
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, bolivar, bongani, prince
1. the owner of the snake is between the bongani-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##2
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
3. the bongani-smoker is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
4. the bolivar-smoker is not the owner of the snake##6
5. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
6. the owner of the fish is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Pet   | frog  | fish | snake | chinchilla  |
| Cigar   | ritmeester | bongani   | prince  | bolivar |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, egyptian, german, argentine
4 different pets are kept: horse, hedgehog, fish, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is not to the left of the owner of the mouse##8
2. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the argentine##5
3. the colombian is the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the argentine is between the colombian and the egyptian##2
5. the egyptian is somewhere between the german and the owner of the horse##7
6. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the egyptian##5
7. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the horse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | german | egyptian          | argentine | colombian     |
| Pet    | fish      | mouse | horse | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: emerald, red, mauve, amber
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, r&b, country, metal
1. the fan of soul is not to the left of the person who likes mauve##8
2. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
5. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5
7. the person who likes amber is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color           | emerald | red | mauve     | amber |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | metal   | soul | country    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, rat, lizard, guinea-pig
There 4 different types of food: peas, nectarine, corn, apricot
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person eating peas is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
3. the person eating corn is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person eating corn##8
5. the owner of the turtle is the person eating peas##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Pet   | lizard   | rat         | guinea-pig   | turtle    |
| Food         | nectarine | apricot | corn | peas |

