.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, prince, dunhill, tiparillo
City: new-york, london, edinburgh, marseilles
1. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the blend-smoker and the prince-smoker##7
2. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
3. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere between the dunhill-smoker and the blend-smoker##7
4. the dunhill-smoker is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
5. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the person traveling to london##7
6. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
7. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
8. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Cigar   | prince   | dunhill | tiparillo | blend    |
| City         | new-york | marseilles   | edinburgh   | london |

