3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
5. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to colone##5
6. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
7. the person traveling to liverpool is the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
