.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, russian, brazilian, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, comedy, action, scientific
1. the person watching comedy movies is not to the left of the russian##8
2. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the japanese and the person watching action movies##7
3. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
4. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
5. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the russian##8
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
7. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | russian      | brazilian | spanish | japanese   |
| Movie-Genre      | thriller | action | scientific  | comedy |

