.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, mouse, rabbit
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, board-games, magic-tricks, sudoku
1. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the owner of the bird##7
5. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the owner of the mouse##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Pet     | bird | mouse | rabbit | frog     |
| Hobby   | woodworking   | magic-tricks        | sudoku          | board-games |

