.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, old-henry, havana, prince
House: farmhouse, tower, ranch-style, victorian
1. the bolivar-smoker is between the prince-smoker and the farmhouse house##2
2. the victorian house is on the far left##1
3. the victorian house is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
4. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
5. the tower house is the tower house##1
6. the havana-smoker is not the ranch-style house##6
7. the prince-smoker is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8
8. the farmhouse house is not to the left of the tower house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Cigar   | prince   | bolivar | havana | old-henry |
| House     | victorian | tower       | farmhouse  | ranch-style    |

