.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, ritmeester, siglo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, february, august
1. the siglo-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's birthday is in march is not the bolivar-smoker##6
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the game-smoker##8
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
6. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | ritmeester | game      | siglo   | bolivar  |
| Birthday   | august    | january | march | february |

