.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower, daffodil, amaryllis
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, december, november, june
1. the person who growsdaffodil is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
2. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
3. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in november##2
6. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Flower    | sunflower        | amaryllis | daffodil      | iris    |
| Birthday   | july | november   | december | june |

