.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, rock-climbing, skydiving, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, firefighter, architect, analyst
1. the analyst is not to the right of the social-worker##8
2. the analyst is not to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##8
3. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the social-worker is somewhere between the architect and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
7. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby   | drawing | rock-climbing         | skydiving    | camping       |
| Job      | firefighter | analyst | social-worker | architect |

