2. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to rome and the person playing bridge##2
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the far left##1
6. the person playing snooker is between the person playing domino and the person playing billiard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| City   | berlin     | san-francisco | rome        | london       |
| Game      | bridge | domino  | snooker | billiard |

