.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, volleyball, handball
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, guinea-pig, goldfish, chinchilla
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 2. the person who's sport is handball is not to the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the right of the owner of the goldfish##8
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##8
10. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Sport          | cricket    | volleyball | surfing | handball |
| Pet   | rabbit | chinchilla  | goldfish     | guinea-pig    |

