.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, western, documentary, action
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, amaryllis, zinnia
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person who growslily##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##8
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who growszinnia is the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person watching western movies is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person watching action movies##2
7. the person watching documentary movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | action        | western | musical | documentary |
| Flower   | zinnia | amaryllis | balloon-flower   | lily    |

