3. the person who growslily is somewhere between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsballoon-flower##7
4. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
5. the person eating grapes is somewhere to the left of the person eating cucumber##5
6. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8
7. the person who growslily is not to the left of the person eating cucumber##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Flower         | zinnia  | balloon-flower | lily  | amaryllis  |
| Food   | tomato | grapes   | cucumber | artichoke |

