.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, librarian, police-officer, dressmaker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, scientific, spy, adventure
1. the person watching scientific movies is not the social-worker##6
2. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the dressmaker is not to the left of the person watching adventure movies##8
4. the police-officer is the person watching action movies##1
5. the dressmaker is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching action movies##7
6. the dressmaker is on the left of the social-worker##1
7. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching adventure movies and the police-officer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Job         | librarian    | dressmaker | social-worker | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | adventure      | spy     | action     |

 